These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, ivory, amber
1. the person who likes ivory is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who likes amber and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Color   | ivory     | lilac    | amber   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, apricot, papaya
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person eating papaya is between the person eating zucchini and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Food     | apricot | papaya | zucchini         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: canasta, billiard, snooker
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the owner of the ferret and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Game   | billiard | canasta     | snooker |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, monopoly
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person playing domino is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person playing monopoly is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Game   | backgammon  | monopoly     | domino |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, trike, train
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the van is between the person driving the train and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Transport     | train    | van | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
House: tower, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the ranch-style house and the tower house##2
2. the tower house is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| House   | tower  | cape-cod   | ranch-style        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
