The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, lacrosse
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person eating pineapple and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Sport   | rowing | skiing | lacrosse     |

