.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, chess
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person playing backgammon is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing chess##2
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | chess   | mah-jongg  | backgammon  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

