There are 3 different nationalities: russian, spanish, mexican
1. the mexican is between the person drinking fanta and the russian##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Nationality       | spanish  | mexican | russian |

