.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, tea
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking juice##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Beverage         | juice | tea | 7up |

