The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, march
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |     3     |
| Pet         | ferret | fish  | rat       |
| Birthday   | november | march | september |

