.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, polish
City: prague, san-francisco, london
1. the person traveling to prague is between the mexican and the polish##2
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian   | polish   |
| City         | london  | prague | san-francisco |

