1. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks       | chess | camping |
| Sport         | badminton | tennis | rowing      |

