2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | zombie | superhero |
| Game   | whist    | mah-jongg | scrabble   |

