.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, orange, emerald
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes emerald and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Color      | emerald | orange   | azure |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 